date: 2026-03-02
command: cargo run --release -p zenjxl-decoder-cli -- --speedtest --num-reps 5 --warmup-reps 2 --num-threads {1,8} --data-type u8 {image}
machine: WSL2 Linux 6.6.87.2 (AMD Ryzen 9 7950X, 32 threads)
purpose: Baseline before safe-parallel refactor. Tests 4K images (from prior work) + new CLIC 2K images.
clic_source: CLIC 2025 originals, encoded with cjxl v0.12.0 at distance 1.0 effort 7
clic_s3: s3://imageflow-resources/test_inputs/jxl/clic_{square,landscape,portrait,wide}_d1.jxl

Speedup summary (8T/1T):
  4K images: 3.9-5.1x
  CLIC 2K:   2.4-2.9x
  tirr_photo: 2.3x (high-detail, smaller)
  bike_web:   3.4x
